  <div class="col-md-7">
    <p>I'd like to share a word or two of thanks to my family. First, I want to sincerely apologize to all of you for always coming up with such crazy ideas, like moving to Ireland or my trip to Australia. Second, I want to thank you for supporting me anyway, with all your strength, and for always being there for me. A special thank you today goes to my dear mom and of course to Rolf, who paid for my dinner tonight. Thank you for that. It was really delicious.</p>
    <p>And now I wish all of you, my dear friends and family, a merry and blessed Christmas from warm and wet Sydney.</p>
